# AI-Based Cognitive Learning Pattern Analyzer (Full Startup Platform)

Refactoring to a production-ready platform with MongoDB, a premium Light Theme, and a multi-language Practice Hub (C, Python, Java).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Database**: **MongoDB** will be the single source of truth for users and cognitive data.
> - **Look & Feel**: **Premium Light Theme** using Tailwind's Zinc and Blue color scales.
> - **Navigation**: Dedicated **Left Sidebar** for core app features and a **Top-Right Dropdown** for profile management.
> - **Active Learning**: Practice modules for **C, Python, and Java** with a custom code execution simulator.
> - **Dashboard**: Unified view with **Wallet Summary** and **Cognitive Analytics**.

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend]
Summary: Implement async MongoDB integration and multi-language support.

#### [NEW] [database.py](file:///d:/Hackathon%20AND%20PROJECTS/Sathyabama%20Hackathon/backend/database.py)
Switch to `motor` for async MongoDB connection.

#### [NEW] [schemas.py](file:///d:/Hackathon%20AND%20PROJECTS/Sathyabama%20Hackathon/backend/schemas.py)
Pydantic models for User, Attempt, Challenge, and Wallet data.

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/Hackathon%20AND%20PROJECTS/Sathyabama%20Hackathon/backend/main.py)
Update all endpoints to use MongoDB and reflect new platform structure.

